				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote11-14445_002_012"><a name="11-14445_002_012"> </a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote11-14445_002_012">11.</a></span>
					<p class="">Véase<a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/ot/isa/1.18?lang=spa#17" target="_blank"> Isaías 1:18</a>.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote12-14445_002_012"><a name="12-14445_002_012"> </a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote12-14445_002_012">12.</a></span>
					<p class="">Véase<a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/nt/luke/15.1-2?lang=spa#0" target="_blank"> Lucas 15:1–2</a>.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote13-14445_002_012"><a name="13-14445_002_012"> </a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote13-14445_002_012">13.</a></span>
					<p class="">Véase<a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/nt/matt/18.11?lang=spa#10" target="_blank"> Mateo 18:11</a>.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote14-14445_002_012"><a name="14-14445_002_012"> </a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote14-14445_002_012">14.</a></span>
					<p class="">Véase<a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/nt/john/8.3-11?lang=spa#2" target="_blank"> Juan 8:3–11</a>.</p>
